{"tid":2009606,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PlayStation國區商店因安全升級即日起停服 索尼致歉","createTime":"2020-05-10T00:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T14:47:28.000Z","uid":163841,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"332291c541706ca58d79933e8b5c61519235bd86","tid":2009606,"uid":163841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:52:41.000Z","msg":"PlayStation國區商店因安全升級即日起停服 索尼致歉<br />\n<br />\n  原標題：索尼致歉！PlayStation國區商店即日起停服：系因安全升級、恢復時間不詳<br />\n<br />\n  來源：快科技<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200510/35113898.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20200510%2F35113898.html&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpZj7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=a33e4bba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200510/35113898.html</a><br />\n<br />\n  在用國行PS4系列主機的朋友注意了，今晨，索尼PlayStation中國官微宣布，中國商店暫時停止服務（5月10日早7點開始）。<br />\n<br />\n  索尼方面公佈的原因是系統安全升級，但奇怪的是，官方並未給出恢復服務的時間，引發玩家的其它猜測。<br />\n<br />\n  通知中，PlayStation中國連續兩次向用戶致歉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15890688069501.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15890688069501.png&h=b445c520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  目前在索尼商城，PS4 500GB定價1999元，PS4 Pro 1TB定價2799元。<br />\n<br />\n  另外，已經發行的實體光碟遊戲包括《侍魂：曉》《西遊記之大聖歸來》《NBA 2K19》《街霸V》《真三國無雙8》《隱龍傳》《地平線：零之曙光》《最終幻想15》《風之旅人》《小小大星球3》《特技摩托：劇變》等有限的幾款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加入防沈迷代碼？"},{"pid":"3841dfe23ef6919ee4a933e85afa9f6a03d3a54a","tid":2009606,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1c48fe2c2a0225230a17116d17dc9ec6f45733","tid":2009606,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541f3f31871007dd4f78550c47bb5481671d5085","